  <datafield tag="520" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
    <subfield code="a">Stochastic quantisation is applied to the problem of calculating real-time evolution on a Minkowskian space-time lattice. We employ optimized updating using reweighting, or gauge fixing, respectively. These procedures do not affect the underlying theory, but strongly improve the stability properties of the stochastic dynamics.</subfield>
